fields.description:
If you create a Story and add Story Point value, then change the Issue Type to Bug the Story Points on the version don't change.

Steps to reproduce:

1. Create an Story and assign it an Story Points value;
2. Check the Planning Board the Story Points for the Version where the issue is added;
3. Change the Issue Type Story to a Bug type;
4. Check the Planning Board and note the Story Points for the Version;

Expectation is that either the change over to a Bug would clear the Story Point field.
